Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:18.91,SeriesTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334.133,309.733)\fad(150,270)}Brave{\fscx900} {\r}Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:24.58,SongOP,,0,0,0,,Over a million of them shine with a blue light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:31.26,SongOP,,0,0,0,,The shards of love have scattered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:38.26,SongOP,,0,0,0,,It's brewing in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:41.22,SongOP,,0,0,0,,A storm that you'll confront
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:44.77,SongOP,,0,0,0,,And because I believe in you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:49.69,SongOP,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:53.90,SongOP,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:57.32,SongOP,,0,0,0,,Courage and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:03.37,SongOP,,0,0,0,,That moment when we join our strength GATHER WAY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.92,SongOP,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:10.29,SongOP,,0,0,0,,I'd almost forgotten it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:18.64,SongOP,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-0.3\q2}The fiery burning and important PASSIONATE feeling in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The mysterious and vast universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In this universe exists the evil life forms, \Nthe space pirates Geisters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,who've invaded Earth in order to obtain the treasures of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,However, in front of the Geisters who use destruction and plunder as they wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:01:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a hero appeared, who completely stood in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the cosmic police, Exkaiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the story of Brave Exkaiser and his friends, who fight against evil all around the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:20.37,EpisodeTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(318.4,391.6)\fad(0,1484)}Aim to Be a Space Pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here at the Space Frontier that has just recently been opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm standing in front of one of its sections called Space Camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a facility that was built in order for children to experience the same training
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and studies of real astronauts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, even though it's a facility for children, full-scale training equipment has been prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Buses full of children who've come to learn from this experience have just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a space shuttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta-kun, can we board that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,After the learning experience, we \Ndo departure training with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! We'll go inside now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This multi-axis trainer is a training device to become familiar with zero gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can experience the zero gravity \Nstate in that space ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta-kun, you know so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's because my dream \Nis to become an astronaut...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But with your grades...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Astronauts fly space shuttles and rockets of latest technology, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that you can't become one unless you're good at math and science!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot Muraoka has said that he wasn't very good at math and science during elementary school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pilot Muraoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who became \Nthe first space pilot in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he's the first in Japan or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but he sure isn't a good pilot then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just be buying a shuttle and hiring a \Nfirst-rate pilot, so it doesn't really matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch the training devices without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't an amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No training touches!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This person is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Muraoka who'll be training you for the next 2 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me remind you that this is a place where you experience astronauts' training and learn from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a playground!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? I'll be relentless so be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as teacher Muraoka says and learn many various things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more like a soccer or\N rugby club's training camp...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who call it hard are fastener nails!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't anything be done about those lame jokes... Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no men or women!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In space, both men and women are in the same conditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um! Can I tell you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We are on Earth now, so the conditions \Nare different from space!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth is also one of the planets in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If Earth would be a spaceship, \Nthen all humans would be astronauts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan! Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You can do it if you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The important thing of an astronaut \Nis challenge mentality!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge mentality?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the mentality to challenge yourself to do anything! That's needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that humans can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try, you can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's challenge, \Ndon't put a lozenge in tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes are spinning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too pitiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, you can't get balance in zero gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No buts or ifs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If Earth would be a spaceship, \Nthen all humans would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Astronauts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know that, then try harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshikawa Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How was this challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Challenges are tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"If Earth would be a spaceship, then all humans would be astronauts"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Let go! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll be docile, I'll let you go. \NWill you be docile?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be docile, so let me go...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you go the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... That wasn't the deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best for humans to be docile!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Young sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But since it's training, it can't be helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like we can go to space immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher Muraoka said that if Earth would be a spaceship, \Nthen all humans would be astronauts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that teacher is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth is also a part of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth might only be a planet that \Nrevolves around sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But Earth has a destination called future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who live here can decide what happens in that future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, if Earth is a spaceship that's going \Nto the future, then mankind is its astronaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all depending on mankind's future actions \Nwhether Earth will become good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially since young Kouta and the others will create the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what he meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same with the challenge mentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The same challenge mentality is needed in order to cultivate both future and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's teacher Muraoka! Exkaiser, good night then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids sleeping in the center of beds and \Nthere's a sleeping empire in Central Asia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that the Empire of Paradise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Re-entry to the atmosphere range requires an angle of inclination of 38 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's in order to suppress the atmosphere's friction heat to the minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, do you have questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:09:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else important for an astronaut \Nbesides the challenge mentality?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Teamwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Teamwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know what you can do alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you need cooperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do spadework!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we'll shortly begin\N the shuttle simulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll finally go to the cockpit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone entered wrongly the re-entry angle's setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not one person's \Nresponsibility, it's everyone's!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a system where even if one makes a mistake, another person checks it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But if everyone acts ignorant, this is what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Teamwork is needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, failure does teach success...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Failure tastes bitter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Change to the next group now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,First up is departure preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the guidelines I taught you and check things with discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the Jack of spades!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Orbiter's output... Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I didn't even do anything yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone touch the switch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! You must calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Geisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Muraoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Muraoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We got shut in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You must think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing in emergencies\N is to calm down and think!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, this is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I must think!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! This time the treasure is ours for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Geisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you try to steal the Space Frontier \Nthat holds humans' future and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,their dreams and hopes of space!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you even do alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Dash Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Drill Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Sky Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Max Team has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Geisters! Prepare yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's your turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's combine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Max Team, Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Triple Fusion, God Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant Fusion, Dragon Kaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do consecutive attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:14:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're inside the shuttle robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently thinking of a way to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so change this Space Frontier back to normal first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As if we'd let you bother us that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bind Crush!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Left&Right Fusion, Ultra Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,God Max, I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ultra Raker! Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Chain Crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,God Sonic-...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,God Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that, it's the end now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a way if you try,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you don't then there's no way at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there an escape pod?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you finally noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Muraoka, you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I'm your instructor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you to notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way too laid-back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This shuttle's whole cockpit is \Nmade to be an escape pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the computer and release the escape pod's safety system.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pilot is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a spare computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan! Connect the spare \Nsystem's circuit immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way to go! Teamwork, teamwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The spare system is connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Releasing the safety system!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This shuttle has turned into a robot!\N It doesn't take our orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You say "no good" too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say "no good" all the time, \Nyou'll turn into a no good man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also too much "buts"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Use those "buts" to rather become \Na man who re{\i1}but{\i0}s nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pilot, don't give up! \NRemember the challenge mentality!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If doing the same thing twice doesn't work, then try something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If the automatic system doesn't work, then how about the manual system?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct! That's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,0!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Departing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Now's the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll back you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,God Max! Ultra Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Cannon Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,God Sonic Buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,King Loader!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Giant Fusion, Great Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta-kun! Looks like we're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! Let's escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.25,0:22:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Muraoka, how did you manage to be calm during that big emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I believed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who believe are saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You all can become great astronauts who operate the spaceship called Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But the "no good" and "but" boy \Ncould train his spirit a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.56,0:22:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to train here for another week?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Um... I won't say "no good" or "but" ever again,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.61,0:22:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:56.23,SongED,,0,0,0,,Faraway wind carries your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:05.32,SongED,,0,0,0,,What could you discover from this excited feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:15.37,SongED,,0,0,0,,Dreams get bigger strongly and fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:23.00,SongED,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to be who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:31.30,SongED,,0,0,0,,Embrace your enthusiastic heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:39.31,SongED,,0,0,0,,And try walking that path
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:46.32,NextEpisodePreview,,0,0,0,,{\pos(323.74,314.667)}NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, have you ever thought \Nthat you wanted a robot friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it would be so much fun to \Nstudy and play together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.79,0:23:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have Exkaiser, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.39,0:24:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I perhaps get brought to the Geisters' base?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.05,0:24:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of Brave Exkaiser,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.35,0:24:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Destruction! Geisters' Base
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.91,0:24:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an alien in your home, too?
